      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out and drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019m really sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely fall in love with it. Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look!",
