    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, a hallmark of naturally aspirated precision. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double-VANOS system for optimized valve timing across the entire power band. This specimen has undergone meticulous preventative maintenance, including documented rod bearing replacement and comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock that ensures peak traction out of technical corners. The exterior retains its factory-original paint depth with no evidence of panel degradation, while the cabin shows zero bolster wear on the Nappa leather. Every bushing, seal, and mechanical interface remains in factory-spec condition, representing a true collector-grade vehicle for the discerning enthusiast who values mechanical purity.",
