      "description": "This 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman S is a true collector-grade specimen that presents exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. Finished in deep Jet Black Metallic, the exterior has been protected since new with a professional-grade ceramic coating, resulting in a mirror-like finish free of rock chips, swirl marks, or blemishes. The interior is equally impeccable; the Agate Grey leather remains supple with no bolster wear, and the cabin still retains that signature new-car scent. This is a single-owner vehicle with only 12,400 miles, exclusively garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and never driven in inclement weather. Mechanically, it is flawless. I have maintained a comprehensive service binder containing every receipt from authorized Porsche dealerships, documenting timely oil changes and a recent spark plug service. The car sits on fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires with nearly full tread. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this Cayman S offers a turn-key experience with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 45900.0,
