    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in museum-quality condition. Powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe, a fully overhauled double-VANOS system, and a precision-shifting 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains rigid with updated bushings and factory-spec Bilstein dampers. Finished in flawless Alpine White over Nappa leather, the vehicle sits on staggered Style 67 alloys with fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. Every mechanical component, from the limited-slip differential to the cooling system, has been maintained to exacting standards. A rare, turn-key specimen for the serious collector.",
